Class Residue

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.openscience.cdk.ChemObject

    Serializable, Cloneable, IAtomContainer, ICDKObject, IChemObject, IChemObjectListener

    public class Residue
extends AtomContainer
    A residue is a named, numbered collection of atoms in an MDMolecule. Residues are used to partition molecules in distinct pieces.
